<br>
<br>
USA give less than 0,25 % of their gross national product to help development in the world.<br>
Maybe you think its too much when it should be at least 0,7% as US promised with the rest of OECD countries.<br>
<br>
In the meantime, 30000 people die everyday in the world because they dont have access to clean water.<br>
You see, i doubt they would give a @#%$ for your better computer.<br>
